Package org.opensky.tools

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Avro2Kml
    OpenSky AVRO to Google Maps KML converter Note: We assume, that messages are more or less ordered by time Generates KML file with flights from avro file.
    Avro2SQLite
    OpenSky AVRO to SQLite converter Note: We assume, that messages are more or less ordered by time Generates SQlite DB with flights from avro file.
    Avro2TestData
    OpenSky AVRO to SQLite converter Note: We assume, that messages are more or less ordered by time Generates SQlite DB with positions and timestamps
    AvroInfo
    Prints useful information about OpenSky avro files
    AvroSort
    Sort entries of OpenSky avro files Note: Ordered messages are needed for decoding positions! Warning: make sure you have enough RAM Outputs avro file with sorted entries.
    AvroSplit
    Read (possibly multiple) OpenSky Avro files and split them to n files.
    ExtractArea
    This file filters data in avro files by geographic area and stores the result in an avro file again.
